==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sternpost
<hw>Stern"post`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>A straight piece of timber, or an iron bar or beam, erected on the
extremity of the keel to support the rudder, and receive the ends of the
planks or plates of the vessel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sternsman</ent>⟦br⟧
